:"RAW_3aee2f2b","title":"从 Agent 到 Skills：AI 智能体架构的范式转变与实战深度解析","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIzOTU0NTQ0MA==&mid=2247559249&idx=1&sn=7cda1453a5f7f51c39f43b76027696a1","date":"2026-03-30 00:31:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/03/RAW_3aee2f2b.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"阿里云开发者","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":61,"score":90},{"id":"RAW_56e0e2c8","title":"2026-03-31 Hacker News Top Stories #","link":"https://supertechfans.com/cn/post/2026-03-31-HackerNews/","date":"2026-03-31 07:52:13","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/03/RAW_56e0e2c8.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"SuperTechFans","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":63,"score":86},{"id":"RAW_06a14ab8","title":"站在“围城”里的库克，手握 2.0 版“苹果税”","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mjc1NjM3MjY2MA==&mid=2691566476&idx=1&sn=1399969d422ece1b36398c93ec2af39b","date":"2026-03-31 00:24:00","oneSentenceSummary":"本文深度解析了苹果在 AI 时代的战略转型：通过将 Siri 打造为开放平台并引入「Siri Extensions」，利用其庞大的硬件生态系统对第三方 AI 服务征收 30% 的新「苹果税」，以空间换取自研模型追赶的时间。","summary":"文章探讨了苹果在 AI 竞争中的独特路径。面对自研模型暂时落后的局面，苹果计划在 iOS 27 中推出「Siri Extensions」，将 Siri 转型为 AI 应用商店，允许用户直接调用 Google Gemini、Claude 等竞争对手的模型。这一举措不仅能防止用户流向其他生态，还能通过 30% 的订阅分成开辟新的营收渠道，即「苹果税 2.0」。同时，苹果将 AI 视为硬件销售的助推器，通过强化 iPhone 17 算力、推出折叠屏手机及智能眼镜等新形态硬件，巩固其「生态围城」。作者认为，苹果正在用其庞大的市场空间换取技术追赶的时间，最终目标是成为 AI 时代的规则制定者。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/03/RAW_06a14ab8.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"腾讯科技","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":13,"score":87},{"id":"RAW_dd5cb7ce","title":"Midjourney 工程师发布开源库 Pretext，旨在革新网页设计","link":"https://venturebeat.com/technology/midjourney-engineer-debuts-new-vibe-coded-open-source-standard-pretext-to","date":"2026-03-30 23:58:37","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/03/RAW_dd5cb7ce.json","topicTag":"frontend-fullstack","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"VentureBeat","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":8,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_15d5fd73","title":"RS